### Pydantic Models

#### [NEW] [karma_models.py](file:///d:/VAYO/matching_system/karma_models.py)

| Model | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `KarmaActionType(str, Enum)` | Mirrors `karma_action_type_enum` |
| `KarmaTier(str, Enum)` | `BEGINNER`, `PATHFINDER`, `EXPLORER`, `CONQUEROR` |
| `KarmaAwardRequest(BaseModel)` | `user_id`, `action_type`, `point_delta`, `reference_id?` |
| `KarmaLedgerEntry(BaseModel)` | Single ledger row for history response |
| `KarmaProfileResponse(BaseModel)` | `user_id`, `karma_score`, `tier`, `tier_label`, `next_tier_threshold?`, `inbox_shield_threshold` |
| `InboxShieldUpdate(BaseModel)` | `threshold: int` (≥ 0) |
| `MessageEligibilityResponse` | `allowed: bool`, `reason?: str` |

Helper: `compute_tier(score: int) → KarmaTier` pure function.

---

### API Routes

#### [NEW] [karma.py](file:///d:/VAYO/matching_system/karma.py)

`APIRouter(prefix="/api/v1", tags=["karma"])`

| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/karma/award` | Clerk JWT | Append ledger row, return `KarmaProfileResponse` |
| `GET` | `/users/{user_id}/karma` | Clerk JWT | Score + tier + paginated ledger |
| `PATCH` | `/users/{user_id}/inbox-shield` | Clerk JWT (self-only) | Set inbox shield threshold |
| `GET` | `/users/{user_id}/karma/can-message/{target_user_id}` | Clerk JWT | Outbound rule + inbox shield check |

---

### Database Manager Extensions

#### [MODIFY] [database.py](file:///d:/VAYO/matching_system/database.py)

Add methods to [DatabaseManager](file:///d:/VAYO/matching_system/database.py#11-206):

- `insert_karma_entry(user_id, action_type, point_delta, reference_id)` — `INSERT INTO karma_ledger`
- `get_karma_score(user_id)` → [int](file:///d:/VAYO/matching_system/database.py#175-201) — reads `karma_score` from `users`
- `get_karma_ledger(user_id, limit, offset)` → list of rows
- `update_inbox_shield(user_id, threshold)` → update `users.inbox_shield_threshold`
- `check_message_eligibility(sender_id, target_id)` → [(allowed, reason)](file:///d:/VAYO/matching_system/database.py#202-206) — compares sender's score vs target's score and inbox shield

